General.Name: Group Up Industrial Co Ltd
General.Description: Group Up Industrial Co., Ltd. manufactures and trades in general boxed-shaped equipment in Taiwan, China, and internationally. The company offers hot air, vacuum, IR drying, hot plate conveyor, and auto conveyor ovens; UV curing, coating machine, exposure, and levelling machines; line integration and other products; roll to roll drying lines, roll to roll laminating machines, roll to roll exposure machines, roll to roll coating drying lines, roll to roll printing drying lines, roll to roll hot press machines, and levelling machines; and robot baking systems. It serves PCB, BGA, FPC, COF, display, touch panel, backlight, solar cell, smart card, optical film, battery, and semiconductor industries. Group Up Industrial Co., Ltd. was incorporated in 1990 and is headquartered in Taoyuan City, Taiwan.
